        <item>
            <title>【教学】ChatGPT 3 个必用免费 GPT　生成图表 + 光速睇 YouTube</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/chatgpt-3-must-use-free-gpt/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=chatgpt-3-must-use-free-gpt</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/chatgpt-3-must-use-free-gpt/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 20 Jun 2024 14:15:30 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ChatGPT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[openai]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1239411</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>日前我们报道过，OpenAI 开放 GPT 商店，免费用户现在也可使用自订 GPT（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/30/openais-gpt-store-is-now-open-for-everyone/ai/">相关报道</a>），体验自订 GPT 的强大功能。GPT 商店是一个平台，允许用户分享及使用各种自订的 GPT 模型。用户可以根据不同的需求和兴趣来调整和应用这些模型。无论你是希望提高工作效率的专业人士，还是对 AI 技术感兴趣的学生，或者只是想寻找娱乐和消遣的普通用户，GPT 商店都有丰富的资源供你选择。</p><p>小编将会详细介绍如何使用 GPT 商店，浏览和选择合适的 GPT 模型，希望通过这篇教学，大家都能够充分利用这项新功能，体验到 AI 技术带来的便利和乐趣。</p><h2>Step 1 开启 GPT 商店</h2><p>首先开启 ChatGPT ，点击「探索 GPT」（绿色框示）进入 GPT 商店。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239459" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-8-599x580.jpg" alt="" width="599" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-8-599x580.jpg 599w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/2-8.jpg 929w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 599px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲开启 GPT 商店</p><h2>Step 2 选择所需 GPT</h2><p>开启「探索 GPT」后，可以看见下图的画面，OpenAI 已经按照不同用途将 GPT 分门别类，视乎你需要用于写作、生产力、研究与分析、教育、日常生活，或是程式设计，你可以选择不同的 GPT 来协助你做事。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239518" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531161726-445x580.jpg" alt="" width="445" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531161726-445x580.jpg 445w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531161726.jpg 690w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 445px" /></p><p>小编选择了写作分类，以「Write For Me」GPT 作示范。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1239535" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-7-502x580.jpg" alt="" width="445" height="514" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-7-502x580.jpg 502w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/3-7.jpg 779w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 445px" /></p><p>点击 GPT 后可以查阅用家对该 GPT 的评分、在分类排行第几位，以及有多少人次使用过。点击「开始交谈」后就能够使用。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1239567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531190040-423x580.jpg" alt="" width="445" height="610" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531190040-423x580.jpg 423w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531190040.jpg 657w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 445px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/29/chatgpt-edit-excel-google-spreadsheet/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】ChatGPT 连结 Google 试算表　可生成各式图表 + 计算数据</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/tinamind/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】AI 中文总结外语网页、YouTube 影片，免 VPN 免费 ChatGPT 网页工具  </a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/13/apple-to-pay-openai-for-chatgpt-through-distribution/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">传 Apple 整合 ChatGPT「零成本」　OpenAI 并未向 Apple 收费</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>Step 3 开始使用</h2><p>现在就可以开始使用 GPT。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1239574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531192756-448x580.jpg" alt="" width="448" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531192756-448x580.jpg 448w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/20240531192756.jpg 695w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 448px" /></p><h2>Diagrams: Show Me</h2><p>这个 GPT 可以帮你生成不同的图表，以图表形式替你介绍不同概念。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242574" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612165903-694x569.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="569" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612165903-694x569.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612165903.jpg 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>小编设想了一个场境，假设我是一个中五程度的中学生，要求 Diagrams: Show Me 以中文生成解释细胞分裂过程的图表。输入指令后，点击绿色框「永远允许」按键，让 Diagrams 生成图表。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242582" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/11-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/11-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/11.jpg 948w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>Diagrams:Show Me 就会按照小编的要求生成一张解释细胞分裂过程的图表（见图一）。小编比较贪心，于是再着 GPT 生成中英对照的图表，亦一样成功（见图二）。如果你觉得在对话框看图时的文字太细，你就可以点击图二绿色框「查看全屏」键，系统会弹出新视窗显示你要求的图表（见图三）。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1242583" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612172426-544x580.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="739" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612172426-544x580.jpg 544w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612172426.jpg 845w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲按照第一次要求生成的图表（图一）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242586" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-6-694x523.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="523" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-6-694x523.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/2-6.jpg 931w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲之后要求中英对照的图表（图二）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242587" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612172844-694x259.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="259" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612172844-694x259.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612172844.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲中英对照的图表（图三）</p><h2>Video Tutor</h2><p>这个 GPT 可以帮你快速看完整条 YouTube 影片，之后再生成撮要、小问答、图表示等，能够帮助用家用 YouTube 更高效学习。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242591" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612173809-694x525.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="525" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612173809-694x525.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612173809.jpg 1189w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>最近 Apple 举行了 WWDC，小编就借用了同事的 WWDC 2024 懒人包影片（<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=L7lfbKX5luE&amp;ab_channel=UNWIRE.HK">影片连结</a>）测试这个 Video Tutor，看看能否做到上述效果。输入指令后，待 GPT 回应你时，同样都是击绿色框「永远允许」按键，让 Video Tutor 与外面的网站交谈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242634" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612190841-694x194.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="194" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612190841-694x194.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612190841.jpg 929w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242635" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3-694x136.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="136" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3-694x136.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/3-3.jpg 945w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲点击「永远允许」</p><p>然后 Video Tutor 就可以替你撮要、提供问题，另外更可显示相关内容出现在影片里的哪个时间点。以下是 Video Tutor 看完影片后生成的回应。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242594" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175103-517x580.jpg" alt="" width="517" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175103-517x580.jpg 517w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175103.jpg 802w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 517px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1242597" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175114-1-541x580.jpg" alt="" width="517" height="554" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175114-1-541x580.jpg 541w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175114-1.jpg 840w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 517px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1242596" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175131-694x404.jpg" alt="" width="517" height="301" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175131-694x404.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612175131.jpg 942w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 517px" /></p><p>在 Video Tutor 生成第一个回应末端会有「Commands」栏目（见上），分别是输入 A 撰写教育文章、D 创建结论图、T 通过多项选择测验来评估我对影片的理解以及 I 指示时间戳。</p><h3>[A] 撰写教育文章</h3><p>小编尝试输入 A 后，看见 Video Tutor GPT 能够将影片内容更加详细地以纯文字方式表达，最后辅以总结。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242605" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180047-594x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180047-594x580.jpg 594w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180047.jpg 922w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1242601" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180102-576x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="598" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180102-576x580.jpg 576w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180102.jpg 893w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180102-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1242602" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180125-541x580.jpg" alt="" width="594" height="636" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180125-541x580.jpg 541w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180125.jpg 840w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 594px" /></p><h3>[D] 创建结论图</h3><p>小编之后再尝试输入「D」，看看 Video Tutor 能够生成甚么样的图表。Video Tutor 生成的图表非常详细，也非常长，亦非常细。有兴趣看看原图的朋友可以点击<a href="https://i.imgur.com/zFfOVXs.png">连结</a>：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242606" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180816-694x372.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="372" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180816-694x372.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612180816.jpg 933w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>[T] 通过多项选择测验来评估我对影片的理解</h3><p>小编之后输入「T」，尝试 Video Tutor 的多项选择测验生成能力，结果显示 Video Tutor 能够生成 5 条看起来有纹有路的多项选择题，回答后 Video Tutor 就会提供正确答案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1242620" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612184116-542x580.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="742" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612184116-542x580.jpg 542w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612184116.jpg 842w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242621" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612184130-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612184130-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612184130.jpg 933w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>小编回答后，Video Tutor 方会提供正确答案。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242629" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/5.jpg 935w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h3>[I] 指示时间戳</h3><p>如果你想重温影片的重点位置，也可以输入「I」，要求 Video Tutor 替你生成具体时间点。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1242632" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612190106-672x580.jpg" alt="" width="672" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612190106-672x580.jpg 672w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240612190106.jpg 917w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 672px" /></p><h2>Universal Primer</h2><p>这个 GPT 可以为你介绍各种不同的知识，让你快速掌握各种概念。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243162" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614173347-694x497.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="497" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614173347-694x497.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614173347.jpg 1100w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>早前小编发现自己的 iPhone 13 升级至 iOS 17 后，可以享受 Qi2 无线充电，可是小编不太清楚 Qi2 与 Qi 有甚么分别，于是就叫 Universal Primer GPT 说明无线充电的原理，并告诉我 Qi 与 Qi2 的分别。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1243177" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614182728-474x580.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="715" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614182728-474x580.jpg 474w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614182728.jpg 735w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 584px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1243178" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614182749-584x580.jpg" alt="" width="584" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614182749-584x580.jpg 584w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614182749.jpg 907w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/20240614182749-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 584px" /></p><p>Universal Primer 会先简单以一段说明甚么是无线充电，随后会详细说明刚才提及的专业字眼，之后会回应小编就 Qi 和 Qi2 差异提出的问题，最后会简单总结内容。如果用家看到这里觉得想深入就这个课题学习，就可以根据 GPT 在总结提出的问题回应。小编觉得这个 GPT 的回应算是简浅容易明白，而且好处是如果要深入了解话题，这个 GPT 可以就不同话题继续分享。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/29/chatgpt-edit-excel-google-spreadsheet/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】ChatGPT 连结 Google 试算表　可生成各式图表 + 计算数据</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/tinamind/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】AI 中文总结外语网页、YouTube 影片，免 VPN 免费 ChatGPT 网页工具  </a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/13/apple-to-pay-openai-for-chatgpt-through-distribution/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">传 Apple 整合 ChatGPT「零成本」　OpenAI 并未向 Apple 收费</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>总结：GPT 种类多　总有一款合你心</h2><p>ChatGPT 开放了 GPT Store 后，大大提升了 ChatGPT 用家的生产力。GPT Store 有不同种类的 GPT，能够为用家生成图片、图表，编写不同风格的文字，亦可充当「哑老师」为用家解惑，更可替用家消化 YouTube 影片，之后再出题测试用家对内容认识程度，最重要的是目前大部份 GPT 均是免费任用，而且预设按照用家评价排列，一般排得前的 GPT 都算实用，甚少会有 AI 以往会出现的「幻觉」问题。当然，使用 GPT 时亦要小心谨慎，不要完全尽信其内容，生成后也要小心覆核。</p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/29/chatgpt-edit-excel-google-spreadsheet/tips-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】ChatGPT 连结 Google 试算表　可生成各式图表 + 计算数据</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/05/23/tinamind/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教学】AI 中文总结外语网页、YouTube 影片，免 VPN 免费 ChatGPT 网页工具  </a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/13/apple-to-pay-openai-for-chatgpt-through-distribution/ai/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">传 Apple 整合 ChatGPT「零成本」　OpenAI 并未向 Apple 收费</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/20/chatgpt-3-must-use-free-gpt/ai/">【教学】ChatGPT 3 个必用免费 GPT　生成图表 + 光速睇 YouTube</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
